Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:31.65,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}听到你这句话的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:36.38,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}脑中一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:43.17,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}身体内游走的火花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:49.78,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}忘记你的所有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:55.81,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}就能继续向前吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:01:01.93,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}不知为何 泪如雨下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:08.38,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}竭尽全力 尽心尽力 活在当下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.30,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}一直是这么过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.42,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}不能说 不能说的再见
